Moksha..

794
01:10:42,938 --> 01:10:43,962
Yodha!

795
01:10:44,073 --> 01:10:45,097
Ó, ne!

796
01:10:45,207 --> 01:10:46,834
Druki, semmi gond. Menj és nézd meg.

797
01:10:52,615 --> 01:10:53,639
Moksha!

